# PWA and Push Notifications Configuration
# =========================================

# VAPID Keys for Web Push Notifications
# Generate your own keys using: npx web-push generate-vapid-keys
# Or visit: https://vapidkeys.com/
NEXT_PUBLIC_VAPID_PUBLIC_KEY=
VAPID_PRIVATE_KEY=
VAPID_SUBJECT=mailto:admin@yourdomain.com

# To generate VAPID keys, run:
# npx web-push generate-vapid-keys

# The public key should be provided to the client (Next.js app)
# The private key should be kept secret on the server

# Example generated keys:
# NEXT_PUBLIC_VAPID_PUBLIC_KEY=BEl62iUYgUivxIkv69yViEuiBIa-Ib9-SkvMeAtA3LFgDzkrxZJjSgSnfckjBJuBkr3qBUYIHBQFLXYp5Nksh8U
# VAPID_PRIVATE_KEY=UUxI4O8-FbRouAf7-7OTt9GH4o-7BgBZi6d7v7v8b8
